1. *Kreveta* je bila uglačana i udobna. (The bed was smoothed and comfortable.)
2. *Krevetu* je trebalo zamijeniti jastuk. (The bed pillow needed to be replaced.)
3. Ona je stavila svoju bebu u *krevetu*. (She put her baby in the bed.)
4. On je prekrio *krevet* zlatnim peškirom. (He covered the bed with a golden towel.)
5. Njene noge su se iskrivile u *krevetu*. (Her legs were curled up in the bed.)